review_title: Fun, but has a few bugs.
one_reviews_text: I'll preface this review by saying I LOVE VR time management and food prep games.  The horror/monster theme of this bar and restaurant simulator is a pretty fun twist on the genre.  I will say there are some bugs that still need to be squashed, but they're minor enough that it isn't game breaking, just slightly annoying when it happens.  If you like cooking sims you'll probably have a lot of fun with this game.
review_feedback: Hi there. Much appreciated your feedback. We would love to know what kind of bugs did you experience. Could you share some more feedback with us?
